# 1 - Serialization
curl http://localhost:8000/snippets/v3

###
curl http://localhost:8000/snippets/v3 \
    -H 'Accept: text/html'

###
curl http://localhost:8000/snippets/v3/1

###
curl -X POST http://localhost:8000/snippets/v3/ \
    -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \
    -d '{"code":"print(\"hello world\")"}'

###
curl -X PUT http://localhost:8000/snippets/v3/2/ \
    -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \
    -d '{"code":"print(\"hello world updated\")"}'